+  // kCCBuiltins output: emit plain C++ functions for a whitelisted subset
+  // of builtins. Three cases:
+  //   1. Not in whitelist         -> Phase-1 comment stub (baseline-fidelity
+  //                                  required for the regression gate).
+  //   2. Whitelisted + JS-linkage -> marker comment; JS linkage deferred to
+  //                                  Phase 3.
+  //   3. Whitelisted + stub-kind  -> real C++ function via CCGenerator,
+  //                                  mirroring the scope + CFG pipeline of
+  //                                  the kCSA path below.
