driven by UNIQUE_INSTANCE_TYPE_MAP_LIST_GENERATOR, emitting
`ReadOnlyRoots(isolate).X_map()` for live cases and UNREACHABLE for
unspecialized. Deferred because no current fixture exercises a
live-branch class.

